========= 8.0.0.035 (beta-testing) =========
Unqiue Version Hash: Blue-Dog-Jane-Cat

add(node-tracking): Ability to disable/enable mesonet information gathering from node-tracking.
add(cimss): Added threshold settings for CIMSS data.

update(documentation): Improved documentation
update(node-tracking): `pin_by_name` is no longer case sensitive
update(node-tracking): Lon/Lat checks are now implemented to prevent tracking spam for stationary nodes.

refactor(node-tracking): refactored node tracking for better maintainability by adding a string reference `tracking_node_message` 
refactor(parsing-utils): Refactored all parsing file names to be more consistent and easier to understand.
refactor(structure.parse): Refactored `structure.parse` to be more maintainable and easier to understand with a defined `cache_keys` list.


future(atmosx-tempest-station): Refactor and redo codebase for maintainability.
future(atmosx-placefile-parser): Refactor and redo codebase for maintainability.